This place was created by the United States Army to test the inteligence of Aliens and Zombies. This huge labyrinth, is an awesome challenge, even for the smartest of the humans.

- 64 spawnpoints
- Secret Teleport
- Kill the monster and get the secret weapon
- Custom textures and props
- Plant the bomb and win 15+ points
